Tavatron:

(OOC: I think I finally caught up, Sinesis is firing on Tav, right? I 
must've missed it, sorry!)

Tavatron growled at Sinesis, the pain in her stomach had increased, but not 
by much.

"Dinobot?! What's wrong?!" Tavatron knew something was definitely wrong this 
time. Dinobot didn't just drop his weapon, something had to be seriously 
wrong. Tavatron fired her optic lasers at Sinesis' chest. She unshesthed her 
staff and held it in a fighting stance.

She knew Dinobot was trying to protect her, and she appreciated it, she 
really did. No one had ever cared enough about her to risk their own welfare 
in exchange for her safety. It was... nice.

Tavatron snarled at Sinesis and fired her optic lasers at him multiple 
times.
